item.title: CVE-2023-6415|2024-10-01T14:49:16.032Z -- voovi%20social%20networking%20script -- voovi%20social%20networking%20script
item.description: A vulnerability has been reported in Voovi Social Networking Script that affects version 1.0 and consists of a SQL injection via signin.php in the user parameter. Exploitation of this vulnerability could allow a remote attacker to send a specially crafted SQL query to the server and retrieve all the information stored in the application.
